I don’t normally write reviews, but given the wonderful  hospitality and amazing staff at this Brooklyn Beer Garden, I would be remiss not to. We had a birthday gathering for my best friend here last night and the staff was super helpful and accommodating every step of the way. The vibe was super chill, the music was perfect and their assortment of beer and wine are a pleasant surprise... but more importantly, they’re in complete compliance with both NYC and CDC guidelines.... they have containers of hand sanitizer everywhere, every group is socially distanced and they limit the number of persons to 50% capacity (so get there early to ensure you get in). Special thanks to Security Staff member, Edgar for the recommendation and to managers Paulina and Gabriel for ensuring everything went smoothly! We’ll def be back many more times!
